未遂犯罰之。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/SLDM/110%2c%e5%af%a9%e7%b0%a1%2c743%2c20211206%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"SLDM,110,審簡,743,20211206,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"審簡","JNO":"743","JDATE":"20211206","JTITLE":"竊盜"}